column4: NSLOCTEXT("[13BE53284AD66D955D7565AF9622AC5B]", "A256BCA64BF561A3DF79A9B869B1BDC2", "A human. Just like you said, Jiji.")
NSLOCTEXT("[13BE53284AD66D955D7565AF9622AC5B]", "25E2F480484D169E9FC99494D706B6EB", "Huh? I thought you knew about Digimon.")
NSLOCTEXT("[13BE53284AD66D955D7565AF9622AC5B]", "209C27754DB50B979673A497FC721AEF", "I got it, this is a dream.")
NSLOCTEXT("[13BE53284AD66D955D7565AF9622AC5B]", "065D50F34CF1C64E7418358E1706FFBF", "Hey wait, you\'re Tokomon. This is a realistic dream.")
NSLOCTEXT("[13BE53284AD66D955D7565AF9622AC5B]", "3BF49273482330910E72A2B0C3EAFAC8", "{Player}, this isn\'t a dream, but it\'s not real either.")
NSLOCTEXT("[13BE53284AD66D955D7565AF9622AC5B]", "BCDE5E0D4EB6483970AAE8A8552F2E80", "What are you talking about? Who are you?")
NSLOCTEXT("[13BE53284AD66D955D7565AF9622AC5B]", "8FF34CD8475649780B7CD7A16013EDFD", "I don\'t know of any Digimon by that name.")
NSLOCTEXT("[13BE53284AD66D955D7565AF9622AC5B]", "991944BC4049FD987628CBB57D7EF5D7", "There are more Digimon than you know of. This is Digimon World.")
NSLOCTEXT("[13BE53284AD66D955D7565AF9622AC5B]", "E81F61324DF630B8C3003F9634ECEDE7", "This world is not a dream nor is it real. It\'s our world.")
NSLOCTEXT("[13BE53284AD66D955D7565AF9622AC5B]", "5EA1D4DA4E155D7686B80EB611B58F6A", "Gee... It looks too real to be a dream.")
NSLOCTEXT("[13BE53284AD66D955D7565AF9622AC5B]", "7107F5EA4024C1FC053C91B635433DC9", "Look behind you, you\'ll see what I mean.")
NSLOCTEXT("[13BE53284AD66D955D7565AF9622AC5B]", "A831397443886E416FC71688ABAAD570", "I remember now! I got sucked into that Digimon key chain.")
NSLOCTEXT("[13BE53284AD66D955D7565AF9622AC5B]", "7FBBA7C749334869CDDA6DA37D7EE152", "I invited you here to save us.")
NSLOCTEXT("[13BE53284AD66D955D7565AF9622AC5B]", "3533F09E4236B0E5C477C281CF37D7FA", "We are in File City, it\'s the center of File Island.")
NSLOCTEXT("[13BE53284AD66D955D7565AF9622AC5B]", "DDEDDC0F4A13ECFD0FA459BCA73F2873", "Well, it was a city. There used to be all kinds of Digimon who lived here.")
NSLOCTEXT("[13BE53284AD66D955D7565AF9622AC5B]", "48F52A7E494AD3DA61F650A2064F8994", "Digimon started to lose heart and moved out of the city.")
NSLOCTEXT("[13BE53284AD66D955D7565AF9622AC5B]", "7947FB3841F757610FF589BBB4F07EE9", "I\'m not sure what caused it. Digimon started losing their speaking skills.")
NSLOCTEXT("[13BE53284AD66D955D7565AF9622AC5B]", "FC09A63348C7CDC9E65885B4F8A767F4", "Some of them still talk, but they all forgot that they lived here.")
NSLOCTEXT("[13BE53284AD66D955D7565AF9622AC5B]", "C4E7996E449A640682C02D9D629CB056", "That\'s what you meant by losing heart.")
NSLOCTEXT("[13BE53284AD66D955D7565AF9622AC5B]", "B63835D5480139E1134F6D9EE9EDB8E1", "You are good at raising Digimon, right?")
NSLOCTEXT("[13BE53284AD66D955D7565AF9622AC5B]", "BC09F788405458C65172CD9B3BFC877D", "Don\'t you realize that you\'re speaking Digimon?")
NSLOCTEXT("[13BE53284AD66D955D7565AF9622AC5B]", "52FCAB224DFCF9057450D3BD6F23CD93", "In this world, your love for Digimon will give you strength.")
NSLOCTEXT("[13BE53284AD66D955D7565AF9622AC5B]", "231446424EA0187E044EC0BFDE77019F", "That\'s why I chose you. You can rally all the Digimon on the island!")
NSLOCTEXT("[13BE53284AD66D955D7565AF9622AC5B]", "C44D67244F840EE65653C0B1645917A9", "Find the cause of this danger and get Digimon to come back.")
